products.title: Skullcandy G.I.
products.description:
The Skullcandy G.I. model is a mid-grade headphone set designed with a heavyweight and durable structure to ensure the headset will hold up even during the most rigorous conditions possible. The fully adjustable headband ensures a firm fit for users of all ages and the headset would prove useful for both casual in home, and travel use. The G.I. model headphone set is equipped with a pair of large size 40mm diameter driver units for enhanced sound. The Skullcandy G.I. headphones include additional features such as a 1.2M cord with a 3.5mm gold plated stereo plug for maximum conductivity, a 6.3mm plug adapter, interchangeable ear-pads, and a travel bag. The headphone set is also available in various different color patterns such as Desert-Camo, Green-Core, Grey-Core, Rasta, Red-Core and Winter-Camo.

Features

  • Over the head headband design with Closed/rest on ear speaker design
  • Fully adjustable headband
  • 6.3mm adapter, interchangeable ear-pads and a travel bag included
  • 1.2M cord with a 3.5mm gold plated stereo plug
  • Available in many different colors; Desert-Camo, Green-Core, Grey-Core, Rasta, Red-Core and Winter-Camo
  • Driver Unit Diameter: 40mm
  • Frequency range: 100 – 18,000 Hz
  • Impedance: 50 ohms
  • Max input power: 400mW

pros.text: Durable, flexible, loud, comfortable, good sound quality, good bass

cons.text: leak sound a lot, vibrate at bass intensive spots in songs, big to carry
cracks within 4 months laser cut aliminium ...not next time im buying senheiser

related.title: Skullcandy Double Agent
related.description:
The Skullcandy Double Agent model is a high end headphone set designed with a closed-ear body and ear port structure. It is targeted for users of all ages who are constantly on the go, but it can also be used casually for home and business. Skullcandy claims the Double Agent headphones present a "hegemonic threat to headphones as we know them". The Double Agent headphones include large size 40mm diameter driver units, designed specifically to give crystal clear highs and booming lows. The headphones also feature a very innovative, built-in SD card slot; which allows users to directly play music on the headset eliminating the dependency on multiple media devices. The Double Agent headphone set includes additional features such as a fully detachable 1 meter USB cable, a fully detachable 1.5 meter standard 3.5mm stereo cable, an included Lithium Ion battery with a maximum of 8 hours run time after a 1.5 hour charge, and the headset is available in various color options.

Features

  • Closed-ear ear port structure
  • Built-in SD card slot; with full support for MP3 file playback
  • Fully detachable USB cable (1M)
  • Fully detachable 3.5mm stereo cable (1.5M)
  • Lithium Ion battery included; 8 hour maximum run time after 1.5 hour charge
  • Available in several different colors; Black, Brown and Green
  • Driver Unit Diameter: 40mm
  • Frequency range: 18 -20,000 Hz
  • Impedance: 32 ohms

pros.text: Great for on the go
Extremely comftorable
Comes with a micro SD card

cons.text: Not the best Frequency response for the price [18 -20,000 Hz]

related.title: Skullcandy iCon
related.description:
The Skullcandy iCon model is a low end sports headphone set designed with a lightweight structure for use during travel and on-the-go occasions. The iCon model is directly related to the Skullcandy Recruit headphone model and is nearly identical. The specially designed and custom built double headband ensures a firm fit for users of all ages. The iCon model headphone set is equipped with a "super powerful" 30mm audio driver for crystal clear sound. The Skullcandy iCon headphones include additional features such as a 45 gram total weight, interchangable caps adorned with special Skullcandy designs for alternate color options, a 1.2M cord with a 3.5mm stereo plug, and Ferrite Magnets. The headphone set is also available in several different color patterns such as Black and Yellow, Chrome, Metal and Red, or Mix.

related.title: Skullcandy MFM Pro
related.description:
The Skullcandy MFM Pro model is a high end headphone set designed with a closed-ear body and ear port structure. It is targeted for users of all ages who are constantly on the go, but it can also be used casually for home and business. Skullcandy claims the MFM Pro headphones are so unique that Marc Frank Montoya (pro snowboarder) selected the model as the single hottest Skullcandy product on the market. The MFM Pro headphones include large size 40mm diameter driver units, designed specifically to give crystal clear highs and booming lows; Skullcandy claims they are "power drivers". The headphones also feature a very innovative, integrated and fully detachable 1 GB flash memory MP3 player; which allows users to directly play music on the headset eliminating the dependency on multiple media devices. The MP3 player slides directly into place on the headset and also eliminates the need for wires. The bundle comes with an optional battery pack for the MP3 player so it may be removed from the headset and used as a standard media device with any pair of headphones. The MFM Pro headphone set includes additional features such as direct USB upload/download to the MP3 player, DJ style headset design with 90 degree swivel speakers, an auxiliary audio jack with a detachable connection cable, and an LCD display complete with a backlight on the MP3 player. The Skullcandy MFM Pro actually has no set release date as of yet.

Features

  • Closed-ear ear port structure
  • DJ Style headband design with 90 degree swivel speakers
  • Built-in 1GB flash memory MP3 player; MP3 player features an LCD display with a backlight
  • Bundle includes optional battery pack for MP3 player so it can be used without the headphones
  • USB direct upload/download for the MP3 player
  • Auxiliary port with fully detachable connection cable
  • Driver Unit Diameter: 40mm

pros.text: top band is very cushy and comfortable
blocks out surrounding sound enough to prevent interferrence
tracks load onto the MP3 player with a quick drag/drop action, very easy
easy to switch tracks on the MP3 player on the fly
ear cups rotate for a snug, comfortable fit that covers the ears without pressing too hard
bass range very well represented, will rattle your teeth

cons.text: big and bulky, a bit awkward to wear outdoors

related.title: Skullcandy Skullcrushers
related.description:
The Skullcandy Skullcrushers model is a mid-grade headphone set designed with a lightweight and portable structure for use during many different occasions; it is suitable for casual in home/business and travel use. The fully adjustable headband ensures a firm fit for users of all ages. The Skullcrushers model headphone set is equipped with a pair of large size 30mm diameter driver units with vibration support that is combined with 30mm Neodymium magnets for enhanced bass; Skullcandy claims the headphones deliver so much bass that carrying this particular headset is like "taking the club with you on the road". The Skullcandy Skullcrushers headphones include additional features such as an in-line vibration level adjustment and on/off switch, a 1.5M cord with a 3.5mm gold plated stereo plug for maximum conductivity, a 6.3mm plug adapter, and a vibration frequency of 100hz.
